citations:
    citation-adwd-tyrion-v:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "Tyrion V"
            text_from_source: "His grey kiss. The thought made his flesh crawl. Death had lost its terror for Tyrion Lannister, but greyscale was another matter."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Tyrion Lannister. The Shy Maid reaches Volantis. Tyrion and Haldon go ashore to gather news at a pleasure house. Tyrion encounters the red priestess Moqorro preaching of Daenerys in the city's plaza. He is recognized as Tyrion Lannister by Jorah Mormont in the pleasure house. Jorah seizes Tyrion, announcing he is taking 'the dwarf' to Daenerys to win his way back into her favor. Tyrion reflects on his fear of having contracted greyscale from the stone man. This is the end of Tyrion's journey on the Shy Maid with Young Griff's company."
